OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with the chance of an
OL,6,Fodd shower in the north at first
OL,7,Fotherwise a mostly dry day with bright
OL,8,For sunny spells. Cloud will increase
OL,9,Fas rain spreads into the west in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly dry with bright or
OL,13,Fclear spells in the east. Cloudy with
OL,14,Frain at times in the west , spreading
OL,15,Feast later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudy with patchy rain in the
OL,18,Fwest at first otherwise mostly dry
OL,19,Fwith bright spells and the odd inland
OL,20,Fafternoon shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
