OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry and bright Monday then cloudy with
OL,7,Fpatchy rain and showers Tuesday. Dry
OL,8,Fat first Wednesday then cloud and rain
OL,9,Fspread east later.
